# Environment Configuration

**Purpose**: Template for environment variables  
**Reference**: quickstart.md, plan.md (technical context)  
**Status**: Use as reference; customize per environment (dev, staging, production)

---

## Copy this file to `.env` and fill in actual values

```bash
# Do NOT commit .env to git (add to .gitignore)
# Each developer/environment should have their own .env file
```

---

## Backend (Spring Boot)

### Database Configuration

```properties
# PostgreSQL connection
SPRING_DATASOURCE_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/ecobook_ia
SPRING_DATASOURCE_USERNAME=postgres
SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD=your_secure_password_here
SPRING_DATASOURCE_DRIVER_CLASS_NAME=org.postgresql.Driver

# Connection pooling (HikariCP)
SPRING_DATASOURCE_HIKARI_MAXIMUM_POOL_SIZE=20
SPRING_DATASOURCE_HIKARI_MINIMUM_IDLE=5
SPRING_DATASOURCE_HIKARI_IDLE_TIMEOUT=600000
SPRING_DATASOURCE_HIKARI_MAX_LIFETIME=1800000

# JPA/Hibernate
SPRING_JPA_DATABASE_PLATFORM=org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQL14Dialect
SPRING_JPA_SHOW_SQL=false
SPRING_JPA_HIBERNATE_DDL_AUTO=validate
```

### Google OAuth2 (Authentication)

```properties
# Google OAuth2 Configuration
# Get these from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials

# OAuth2 Client ID (for web backend)
OAUTH2_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id.apps.googleusercontent.com

# OAuth2 Client Secret (KEEP PRIVATE!)
OAUTH2_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here

# Redirect URI (must match Google Console configuration)
OAUTH2_GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/callback
# Production: https://api.ecobook.com/api/v1/auth/callback

# Token endpoint
OAUTH2_GOOGLE_TOKEN_URI=https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token
OAUTH2_GOOGLE_USERINFO_URI=https://openidconnect.googleapis.com/v1/userinfo
```

### JWT (Token Management)

```properties
# JWT Secret Key (generate with: openssl rand -base64 32)
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_base64_encoded_here

# JWT Expiry (7 days in milliseconds)
JWT_EXPIRY_MS=604800000

# JWT Refresh Token Expiry (14 days, optional)
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRY_MS=1209600000
```

### Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)

```properties
# Firebase Configuration
# Download from: https://console.firebase.google.com/project/[PROJECT_ID]/settings/serviceaccounts/adminsdk

# Firebase Service Account JSON (full path)
FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON=/path/to/firebase-service-account.json

# Or as inline environment variable (base64 encoded)
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_BASE64=<base64_encoded_json>

# Firebase Project ID
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_firebase_project_id
```

### Google Gemini API (AI Classification)

```properties
# Gemini API Key
# Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikeys

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Gemini API Timeout (seconds)
GEMINI_API_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=10

# Circuit Breaker Configuration (Q7)
GEMINI_CIRCUIT_BREAKER_FAILURE_THRESHOLD=10
GEMINI_CIRCUIT_BREAKER_WINDOW_MINUTES=5
GEMINI_CIRCUIT_BREAKER_PAUSE_SECONDS=30
```

### Image Storage

```properties
# Local Filesystem Storage (MVP)
IMAGE_STORAGE_TYPE=local
IMAGE_STORAGE_PATH=/uploads

# Or S3 (future Phase 2+)
# IMAGE_STORAGE_TYPE=s3
# IMAGE_STORAGE_S3_BUCKET=ecobook-materiais
# IMAGE_STORAGE_S3_REGION=us-east-1
# IMAGE_STORAGE_S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_aws_access_key
# IMAGE_STORAGE_S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_aws_secret_key

# Image limits
IMAGE_MAX_SIZE_MB=5
IMAGE_ALLOWED_TYPES=image/jpeg,image/png
```

### Logging & Monitoring

```properties
# Logging
LOGGING_LEVEL_ROOT=INFO
LOGGING_LEVEL_COM_ECOBOOK=DEBUG
LOGGING_FILE=/var/log/ecobook-backend.log
LOGGING_FILE_MAX_SIZE=10MB
LOGGING_FILE_MAX_HISTORY=30

# Structured Logging (Phase 2+)
# LOGGING_FORMAT_JSON=true
```

### Application Server

```properties
# Spring Boot Server
SERVER_PORT=8080
SERVER_SERVLET_CONTEXT_PATH=/api/v1

# CORS Configuration (for Android app)
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:*,https://*.ecobook.com

# API Documentation (Springdoc-OpenAPI)
SPRINGDOC_SWAGGER_UI_ENABLED=true
SPRINGDOC_SWAGGER_UI_PATH=/swagger-ui.html
```

### Rate Limiting

```properties
# Per-user rate limits (tokens bucket)
RATELIMIT_UPLOADS_PER_HOUR=10
RATELIMIT_SEARCHES_PER_MINUTE=100
RATELIMIT_API_REQUESTS_PER_HOUR=5

# Global rate limit for Gemini calls
RATELIMIT_GEMINI_PER_DAY=250
```

### Email Configuration (Future V2)

```properties
# SMTP for email notifications
SPRING_MAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SPRING_MAIL_PORT=587
SPRING_MAIL_USERNAME=notifications@ecobook.com
SPRING_MAIL_PASSWORD=your_smtp_password
SPRING_MAIL_PROPERTIES_MAIL_SMTP_AUTH=true
SPRING_MAIL_PROPERTIES_MAIL_SMTP_STARTTLS_ENABLE=true
```

---

## Android (Mobile App)

### Google OAuth2 (Client)

```properties
# Android OAuth2 Configuration
# Get from: Google Cloud Console (Android app credentials)

# OAuth2 Client ID (for Android)
ANDROID_OAUTH2_CLIENT_ID=your_android_client_id.apps.googleusercontent.com

# Redirect Scheme (for deep linking)
ANDROID_OAUTH2_REDIRECT_SCHEME=ecobook://auth

# OAuth2 Scopes
ANDROID_OAUTH2_SCOPES=openid,email,profile
```

### Firebase (FCM Token & Cloud Messaging)

```properties
# Firebase Configuration (generated from Google Cloud Console)
# Download google-services.json and add to app/

# Firebase Project ID
ANDROID_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_firebase_project_id

# Firebase Messaging Sender ID
ANDROID_FIREBASE_SENDER_ID=your_firebase_sender_id

# Firebase API Key
ANDROID_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_firebase_api_key
```

### Backend API Configuration

```properties
# Backend API Base URL
ANDROID_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api/v1
# Production: https://api.ecobook.com/api/v1

# API Timeouts (milliseconds)
ANDROID_API_CONNECT_TIMEOUT_MS=10000
ANDROID_API_READ_TIMEOUT_MS=30000
ANDROID_API_WRITE_TIMEOUT_MS=30000

# API Retry Configuration
ANDROID_API_RETRY_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3
ANDROID_API_RETRY_BACKOFF_MULTIPLIER=2
```

### App Configuration

```properties
# App Name & Version
ANDROID_APP_NAME=EcoBook IA
ANDROID_APP_VERSION=1.0.0
ANDROID_APP_BUILD_TYPE=debug
# Production: ANDROID_APP_BUILD_TYPE=release

# Minimum SDK Version
ANDROID_MIN_SDK=26

# Target SDK Version
ANDROID_TARGET_SDK=34
```

### Feature Flags (A/B Testing / Phase Rollout)

```properties
# Feature toggles
ANDROID_FEATURE_GEMINI_ENABLED=true
ANDROID_FEATURE_FCM_ENABLED=true
ANDROID_FEATURE_IMAGE_COMPRESSION=false  # Phase 2+
ANDROID_FEATURE_OFFLINE_SYNC=false       # Phase 2+
```

### Analytics & Monitoring (Phase 2+)

```properties
# Firebase Analytics
ANDROID_ANALYTICS_ENABLED=false

# Crashlytics
ANDROID_CRASHLYTICS_ENABLED=false

# Custom Events Tracking
ANDROID_TRACKING_ENABLED=false
```

